The Ogun State House of Assembly has passed a bill seeking to alter the nomenclature of the Tai Solarin College of Education (TASCE) to Sikiru Adetona College of Education, Science and Technology, Omu-Ajose, Ijebu. The institution is being renamed after the Awujale, Oba Sikiru Adetona. the paramount ruler of Ijebuland. The bill was passed into law after the Chairman of the House Committee on Education, Science and Technology, Ademuyiwa Adeyemi, presented the report of his committee on the bill during plenary on Thursday. 